  "text": "The GenBank accession number was AF395008 for the reference genomic sequence used for IL-4 alignments. The IL-4 SNP polymorphism at position -590C/T (rs2243250) was genotyped by PCR-RFLP analysis according to previously published methods [CITATION_1] ∘ C for 1 min. The last synthesis step was extended to 10 min at 72 ∘ C. Amplified products were separated on 2% agarose gel; the size of the product corresponds to the number of the repeats present (allele 1 = 3 repeats (254 bp); allele 2 = 2 repeats (184 bp)). The rarely occurring allele type 3 with only a single repeat (114 bp) was not present in our set.",
